<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>404 - Page Not Found | Funki</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #0d0d0d;
            color: #cccccc;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: #00ffff;
            margin: 0;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        a {
            color: #00ffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #00ffff;
            color: #0d0d0d;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #888;
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="logo">funki.com</div>
    <h1>Funki.com</h1>
    <h2 style="color: White;">404</h2>
    <p>Oops! The page you're looking for doesn't exist.</p>
    <a href="/funki/auth">Go Back Home</a>
</body>
</html>
